short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Goto Jira tickets by providing Jira key

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
While working with Jira, users have to open a large number of SDICX tickets daily (especially for Product Owners and Managers).

This extension helps users to open SDICX tickets and other Jira items quickly by providing ticket number (e.g. 44125) or Jira item key (e.g. IT-112) and then press Enter to access.
